data.description: Welcome to a meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 3-bathroom haven nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac. This charming home boasts a newly extended kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a stylish design. The generously lit living room is perfect for relaxation, while each bedroom, including a large master with an ensuite, comes equipped with a walk-in closet. Life Proof flooring in the loft and bedrooms combines both style and durability. The fully fenced backyard, complete with a deck, offers a private outdoor oasis surrounded by a lush Green Belt. Storage needs are met with a spacious shed featuring two lofts, drywall insulated for convenience. Enjoy the tranquility of this location, with a park less than a mile away. This property seamlessly blends upgraded features with a convenient location, making this an ideal home for those seeking comfort and style in Thornton.
